translation: Break through the Cathedral City's defenses.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Break through the Cathedral City's defenses.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: The disciple Cent has joined the fight.{#Name="説明文"}
source: The disciple Cent has joined the fight.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: La la la la! La la, la la la lu lu lu...  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier B"}
source: La la la la! La la, la la la lu lu lu...  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Lu-lu...huff huff huff huff...lu... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Lu-lu...huff huff huff huff...lu... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Fo! Fo, fo...huff huff... Urrrrgh! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Fo! Fo, fo...huff huff... Urrrrgh! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Su-su su su-su-su ssst! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Su-su su su-su-su ssst! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Sta-ta-suuu, sutaaa ssst su-su...  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Sta-ta-suuu, sutaaa ssst su-su...  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Gorrrh! Grip grap grurrrrrpp!  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Gorrrh! Grip grap grurrrrrpp!  (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Fah salahasala, sa, saahaaaa... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Fah salahasala, sa, saahaaaa... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Kill youuuuu youuuu youuu yaaaaa! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Kill youuuuu youuuu youuu yaaaaa! (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Huff huff huff... S-So...strong.... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Huff huff huff... S-So...strong.... (insane ranting){#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: Significant anomalies have been observed in{LF}the group of singularities centered around Zero.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Significant anomalies have been observed in{LF}the group of singularities centered around Zero.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: Mikhail, meant to be the group's harmonizing factor,{LF}has devolved and demonstrated other anomalous behavior.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Mikhail, meant to be the group's harmonizing factor,{LF}has devolved and demonstrated other anomalous behavior.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: Both the Intoners and their disciples seem to be{LF}entering unstable mental and emotional states.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Both the Intoners and their disciples seem to be{LF}entering unstable mental and emotional states.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: I shall continue my investigation,{LF}keeping an eye out for any signs of a Full Collapse.{#Name="Accord"}
source: I shall continue my investigation,{LF}keeping an eye out for any signs of a Full Collapse.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: I know. I can't even make fun of 'em. {#Name="Dito"}
source: I know. I can't even make fun of 'em. {#Name="Dito"}

translation: Commoners so often pick the wrong person{LF}to devote themselves to, you know?{#Name="Cent"}
source: Commoners so often pick the wrong person{LF}to devote themselves to, you know?{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Ho ho! This is quite the conundrum.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Ho ho! This is quite the conundrum.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: It's hard to come up with a pithy retort when{LF}you can't even understand what they're saying.{#Name="Octa"}
source: It's hard to come up with a pithy retort when{LF}you can't even understand what they're saying.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: あ、すまん。つい、ヤツらにつられて……{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: あ、すまん。つい、ヤツらにつられて……{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: Ho ho! This is quite the conundrum.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Ho ho! This is quite the conundrum.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Hey! I'm here! I'm here to help!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey! I'm here! I'm here to help!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Good. Just...uh...try not to push yourself.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Good. Just...uh...try not to push yourself.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?{LF}I'm gonna try double hard!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?{LF}I'm gonna try double hard!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I'm gonna try double hard like I always do!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm gonna try double hard like I always do!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: You can't run forever. I WILL find you.{#Name="Zero"}
source: You can't run forever. I WILL find you.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: And when I do, sweet sisters,{LF}I'm gonna tear you both apart!{#Name="Zero"}
source: And when I do, sweet sisters,{LF}I'm gonna tear you both apart!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Get that fucking curse off my dragon!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Get that fucking curse off my dragon!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: She's been consumed by her song.{#Name="Zero"}
source: She's been consumed by her song.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ugggh... This is all my fault...{#Name="Cent"}
source: Ugggh... This is all my fault...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: If only... If only I hadn't left her...{#Name="Cent"}
source: If only... If only I hadn't left her...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: I suppose... I can at least end her misery...{#Name="Cent"}
source: I suppose... I can at least end her misery...{#Name="Cent"}

translation: Ha ha ha! This isn't like you at all, Cent!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Ha ha ha! This isn't like you at all, Cent!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Never thought I'd see you sympathizing{LF}with a whack-job Intoner!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Never thought I'd see you sympathizing{LF}with a whack-job Intoner!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Welp, I guess one weirdo attracts another.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Welp, I guess one weirdo attracts another.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Aaah ha ha ha ha ha!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Aaah ha ha ha ha ha!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: I'm here! I'm here and I'm gonna try real hard!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I'm here! I'm here and I'm gonna try real hard!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: I've had enough of this shit, Two!{LF}I want my dragon back!{#Name="Zero"}
source: I've had enough of this shit, Two!{LF}I want my dragon back!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I want him back, and I want him back NOW!{#Name="Zero"}
source: I want him back, and I want him back NOW!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Could you die now? I mean, like, really die?{#Name="Dito"}
source: Could you die now? I mean, like, really die?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Don't act so goddamn happy, freak!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Don't act so goddamn happy, freak!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Killing Two didn't break your curse.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Killing Two didn't break your curse.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: So I have to kill One.{#Name="Zero"}
source: So I have to kill One.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I have to kill all the Intoners.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I have to kill all the Intoners.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: But... But I can be okay like this!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: But... But I can be okay like this!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: One's going to pay for this.{#Name="Zero"}
source: One's going to pay for this.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: One of my sisters must be big into dogs.{#Name="Zero"}
source: One of my sisters must be big into dogs.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Come here, mutt! I got a doghouse for ya...in hell!{#Name="Dito"}
source: Come here, mutt! I got a doghouse for ya...in hell!{#Name="Dito"}
